@startuml
autonumber
actor "User" as User
participant "MaintenanceController" as Ctrl
participant "QueryService" as Service
participant "Repository" as Repo

User -> Ctrl : GET /api/maintenance/search?filters...
activate Ctrl
note right of Ctrl: Delega a consulta complexa\npara o Service.
Ctrl -> Service : searchRecords(filters, pageable)
activate Service
Service -> Repo : searchRecords(filters, pageable)
activate Repo
Repo --> Service : Page<MaintenanceRecord>
deactivate Repo
Service --> Ctrl : Page<MaintenanceRecord>
deactivate Service
Ctrl --> User : 200 OK (Page Content)
deactivate Ctrl
@enduml